Italiano
We do not collect or store user's personal information. We don't require you to provide any information.
We have access to the information about the devices running our apps, only in aggregate and anonymized form (e.g., number of downloads per Country, number of purchases, crashes, ...). We are not able to connect this information to a specific person or device.
Some of our apps are supported by ads, and to help us provide you with the best service, we work with third party analytics. You can check their privacy policies at the following addresses:
Google AdMob and Analytics:
www.google.com/intl/policies/policies/privacy
Apple:
www.apple.com/legal/privacy/en-ww
Microsoft:
privacy.microsoft.com/en-us/privacystatement
AppLovin:
www.applovin.com/privacy
How Google uses data when you use our apps
We provide support by email. When you ask for support, the information you send us are used only for this purpose. We do not give this information to other entities.